      "content": "i know, but the pain is so constant that i feel like waiting 6 or 8 hours between doses is just letting the pain win. if i take a 400mg one every 2 hours, it's basically just staying at a steady level in my system, right? wouldn't that actually be more effective for managing the inflammation than letting it spike?",
